4. Start MongoDB server locally:
   mongod

5. Run the program:
   node 6A.js

6. Test API using Postman:

- Create User (POST):
  URL: http://localhost:3000/users
  Body (JSON):
  {
    "name": "Alice",
    "email": "alice@test.com"
  }

- Get Users (GET):
  URL: http://localhost:3000/users

- Update User (PUT):
  URL: http://localhost:3000/users/<user_id>
  Body (JSON):
  {
    "name": "Alice Updated",
    "email": "alice.new@test.com"
  }

- Delete User (DELETE):
  URL: http://localhost:3000/users/<user_id>

